1
00:00:00,350 --> 00:00:01,190
Can you hear me?

2
00:00:01,410 --> 00:00:02,350
It's Dr. Morgan.

3
00:00:02,670 --> 00:00:04,490
Your delusions almost took the life from you

4
00:00:04,490 --> 00:00:04,990
this time.

5
00:00:05,910 --> 00:00:07,830
My face, it's in bandages.

6
00:00:08,830 --> 00:00:09,810
Where am I?

7
00:00:10,630 --> 00:00:13,350
Who am I?

8
00:00:13,450 --> 00:00:15,390
You must have thought you had somewhere important

9
00:00:15,390 --> 00:00:16,790
to go when you stole that car.

10
00:00:16,950 --> 00:00:17,570
Oh, no.

11
00:00:17,890 --> 00:00:19,050
You did a lot of damage to that

12
00:00:19,050 --> 00:00:20,270
face of yours in the crash.

13
00:00:20,790 --> 00:00:21,450
I'm sorry.

14
00:00:21,710 --> 00:00:22,990
I can't believe...

15
00:00:22,990 --> 00:00:23,690
No apologies.

16
00:00:24,050 --> 00:00:25,630
All we need is your best effort.

17
00:00:26,610 --> 00:00:29,390
And before you can give us that, you

18
00:00:29,390 --> 00:00:30,250
need some rest.

19
00:00:31,310 --> 00:00:33,670
Bruce, help our lad back to his room.

20
00:00:34,250 --> 00:00:34,970
Don't worry, son.

21
00:00:35,630 --> 00:00:36,690
We'll talk again soon.

